data.description: One story, full brick, open floor plan, large family room has stone fireplace w/gas logs, master suite has whirlpool tub, separate shower & large walk-in/wrap around closet, split bedrooms, pullman bath with double sinks, office off front entry that could be 4th bedroom (with closet), half bath, laundry room w/folding table, covered patio, pergola, oversized storage shed. Neighborhood pool & park, minutes to Bixby West Elementary & Intermediate School. Close to Kimberly Clark.
